{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "12.1",
      "line_index": 12,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b0280ca",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "次は……この結婚を推したいと思ってるんです！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "14.0",
      "line_index": 14,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "48f1817c",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "どんなプランなんだ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "16.1",
      "line_index": 16,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9def9596",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "ズバリ、宇宙婚ならではのプラン……宇宙遊泳婚です！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.1",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2155cefb",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "宇宙遊泳……婚？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.0",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b27de01a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "宇宙遊泳って、宇宙に出るってことだよな？　……でもそれって、確かリリアンしか出来ないんだろ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.1",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "20b53bac",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "それは恐らく、体表コーティングでの宇宙活動のお話ですね？　非リリアンの方でも問題なく動くための服がございますのでご安心ください！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "27.0",
      "line_index": 27,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "def67816",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ブライダルがどこからか、１着の服を取り出す。銀色でテカテカとした変わった服だが、これを着れば宇宙空間に出られるのだろうか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "29.0",
      "line_index": 29,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "583cd2e6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "それは面白そうだな……結婚が、というか、外に出られるってことが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "31.0",
      "line_index": 31,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "56720985",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……構造とか、聞いたら教えてもらえたり？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.1",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4e5f098f",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "生憎とそちらの専門家ではございませんので……申し訳ございません",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "35.0",
      "line_index": 35,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "156b0e5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そ、そうか……分解とか出来れば、助かるんだけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "37.1",
      "line_index": 37,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a12c9454",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "こっ、高価な物なのでご遠慮いただけますと……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "39.0",
      "line_index": 39,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "98095512",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "くっ……残念だ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "41.1",
      "line_index": 41,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f521d574",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "では……次はどなたと結婚してみますか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "43.0",
      "line_index": 43,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "22d6c29a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "えっ、うーん……ブルームは……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "50.1",
      "line_index": 50,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "67a0732",
      "speaker": "ブルーム",
      "ja": "ぜったい、お断り！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "52.0",
      "line_index": 52,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1dac868e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（だよな。またリズと、っていうのも変な感じになるかも知れないし……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.1",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ccbb9d9d",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "ドレスはまだございますよ。リリアンサイズの物は１着だけですが！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.0",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "753d2f4b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そうなのか……う、うーん……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.1",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1af81bb",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "（……ルミナ、{G_PlayerName}の許嫁って言ってたくらいだし、結婚……真似だったとしても、してみたいはずよね？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.1",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "60d15752",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "（……今までルミナは辛い生活してて、ブライダルもルミナが呼んだんだから！　これくらい、あたしも我慢しないと……！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.1",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e3d2d326",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ねえ！　じゃあルミナが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.1",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9936f847",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "コハルさんと、したほうがいいと、思う！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.0",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c1231e5f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルの声を遮るように、ルミナが声を上げる。……いつものルミナの声量を考えると、張り上げる、と言ったほうが近いかもしれない。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.1",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ba7c3a18",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ど、どうしたのルミナ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.1",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1ea84efa",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "あっ、ご、ごめんなさい……えっと、私は前……ひな祭りの時に着物を着せてもらった、から。今回は、コハルさんのほうがいいかなって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.1",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2cd4b27b",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そ、そう？　でも……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "87.0",
      "line_index": 87,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a59b1535",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……いいんじゃないか、コハル。せっかくルミナがこんなに言ってくれてるんだし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.1",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "fb9acc3f",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "……いいのかしら",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.0",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1b2fa024",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "それにコハルだって、村で結婚式する時は毎回、あんなドレスが着てみたい～って騒いでたじゃないか。小さい時は泣きわめいて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.1",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a43195f6",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "うううっ、うるさいわね！　子供の時の話でしょ！？　わ、わかったわよ、やればいいんでしょ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.1",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4370972",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "コハル様でございますね！　では、こちらへいらしてください！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.1",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ecea7bf9",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "…………",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "105.0",
      "line_index": 105,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "23042da6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ルミナ、大丈夫か……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.1",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "155200dc",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "えっ。う、うん。大丈夫だけど……どうか、した？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "109.0",
      "line_index": 109,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "eac22913",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いや、あんな大きな声出すのって珍しいからさ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.1",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b37b09bb",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "……コハルさんのドレス姿が見たかった、だけだよ。ありがとう……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "113.1",
      "line_index": 113,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e9f6eca1",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "（……ああでも、しないと。自分が、何するかわかんなかったから……って言ったら。{G_PlayerName}くん、軽蔑するかな……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "120.1",
      "line_index": 120,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3cb25b82",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "…………男。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "122.0",
      "line_index": 122,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b16f6033",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ど、どうしたんだよ雫。近いぞ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.1",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "242e9048",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "……殺しますよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.0",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b844796d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いつにも増して理不尽！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bbd96853",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "およそ１０分後……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "142.1",
      "line_index": 142,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2e79fd65",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "さあさあコハルさん！　恥ずかしがらないで、こちらへ！　是非！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.0",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "47fe8c1",
      "speaker": "コハルの声",
      "ja": "うう……やっぱり似合わないんじゃ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "146.1",
      "line_index": 146,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "601bb336",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "とてもお似合いですってば！　さあさあ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.1",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5232c5bd",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "…………おまたせしました",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "162.0",
      "line_index": 162,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "46e3c503",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……おお……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "164.0",
      "line_index": 164,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7643fbf0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ドレスに身を包んだコハルが、おずおずと姿を現す。何か感想を言おうとしたが、言葉が何故かでてこない。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "166.1",
      "line_index": 166,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "692f5a11",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "何よ、おお……って",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "168.0",
      "line_index": 168,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d48561d0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "え？　あ、ああ……うん。似合ってるぞ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "170.1",
      "line_index": 170,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "119931ef",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "本当に～？　ウソついてないでしょうね？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "172.1",
      "line_index": 172,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a12fe766",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "……なーんて、あんたがウソついたらすぐわかるけどね。ありがと！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.0",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c10cd6a4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "今更お世辞なんか言うかっての。……いや、動きはぎこちないと思うけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.1",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "68ddccb4",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "しょーがないでしょ！？　こんな良いドレス、初めてなんだから！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "189.1",
      "line_index": 189,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "50f808b0",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "コハルさん、すごい……綺麗……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "191.1",
      "line_index": 191,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3b0ecdf8",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "くっ……！　ルミナ様、お許しください……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.1",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ab5c390b",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "ど……どうしたの？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.1",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "708154a2",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "本来であれば、ルミナ様の写真しか存在を許さない、情報端末の記憶領域に……コハル様の写真を収めるとは……！　くっ……しかし、抗えない……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.1",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e0b9e2bf",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "え……うん……好きなだけ撮ったら、良いと思うな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "205.1",
      "line_index": 205,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "85528f1",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "いやー、お綺麗ですよね、コハル様！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "207.1",
      "line_index": 207,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "fff5f2a4",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "あ……ブライダル、さん。はい……綺麗、ですね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "209.1",
      "line_index": 209,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "150adaa1",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "ルミナ様も、次の機会は是非！　私どものほうでドレスを作らせてください！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "211.1",
      "line_index": 211,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "434a718e",
      "speaker": "雫",
      "ja": "ルミナ様専用のドレス……！？　素晴らしい！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "213.1",
      "line_index": 213,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "1076fc56",
      "speaker": "ルミナ",
      "ja": "あ、あはは……ありがとう……お願い、しようかな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "221.1",
      "line_index": 221,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "12222dad",
      "speaker": "リズ",
      "ja": "宇宙服とやらの準備が出来たが",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "223.1",
      "line_index": 223,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4c8af48e",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "リズさん、ありがとうございます！　コハル様！　{G_PlayerName}様！　準備が出来ましたので、移動いたしましょう！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "233.1",
      "line_index": 233,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "48d995db",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あ、はーい！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "235.0",
      "line_index": 235,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "971a465a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いよいよ、宇宙か……！　ドキドキするな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "237.1",
      "line_index": 237,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "758d3d8b",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ね！　あたしも最初は緊張したわ！　でも大丈夫、あたしがリードしてあげるから！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "245.0",
      "line_index": 245,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f8a9c5a8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（……宇宙に出ることに、ドキドキしてる……んだよな？　これ……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "251.0",
      "line_index": 251,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "436b1a84",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "釈然としない思いを抱きながらも、コハルに続いて移動することにした。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "267.0",
      "line_index": 267,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "50b8a88a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お、お、お……ゆ、揺れる……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "271.1",
      "line_index": 271,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7d92820f",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "大丈夫？　手を離さないようにね！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "273.0",
      "line_index": 273,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7b261beb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "宇宙服を着て、初めての宇宙遊泳……は良いのだが、ゆらゆらと揺れて落ち着かない。どちらが上で下なのやら……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "280.1",
      "line_index": 280,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f767a17c",
      "speaker": "ブライダル",
      "ja": "ではお二人共、式を始めます！　よろしいですか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "282.1",
      "line_index": 282,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e9fbda63",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "はい！　……大丈夫？",
