      "line_hash": "9bc0d4b8",
      "speaker": "ブルーム",
      "ja": "クソ人間、軟弱～！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "413.0",
      "line_index": 413,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a5bbcd8b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "し……仕方ないだろ……初めての宇宙遊泳だったんだか……おえぇ……",
      "zh": ""
